{"tid":1026692,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱落大雨喺吐露港揸車真係痴線","createTime":"2019-02-18T09:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T04:45:24.000Z","uid":135734,"like":2,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"01565c2353c914fef92a30b3230e812df81d2408","tid":1026692,"uid":135734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:56:18.000Z","msg":"新牌未遇過咁大雨 喺大埔揸翻上水 開咗雨撥 但完全睇唔到前面 地下啲線又睇唔到 勁驚但又唔停得 打死火燈繼續揸 去到粉嶺前少少先細雨睇得翻野<br />\n<br />\n想問 究竟係我開唔夠大冷氣/吹風落玻璃搞到玻璃起霧，定係真係超級大雨嘅時候 能見度真係會咁低？<br />\n真係乜都睇唔到咁滯"},{"pid":"93e1f3de0557ca14ba089db77e2cd429810bc743","tid":1026692,"uid":161990,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:58:05.000Z","msg":"我果陣開大雨撥 同揸慢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申5年雪櫃牌"},{"pid":"37379d87147636d32f03ed7e5fb89d2e4aaebe13","tid":1026692,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:58:22.000Z","msg":"水撥開幾多格?<br />\n冷氣唔係大唔大嘅問題，而係你有冇校啱"},{"pid":"f8bcc5a81df07b3f2ce87b9105450a0852767cf9","tid":1026692,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"渣慢d"},{"pid":"50dc544439adf6bcec4fd2b600cda879c7592796","tid":1026692,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"馬路炸彈"},{"pid":"78069b68b1879d8a322f7bf8350515249e034d8b","tid":1026692,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58551189143fb2e6d1f588077c6c3c66f843fb1a","tid":1026692,"uid":109515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"巴打你令我諗起幾年前美麗華出面見到架P 牌七人車，嗰日又係有雨，架車前後玻璃起曬霧，又開咗雨撥同大燈，最搞笑係線都逆埋仲要揸得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fe18a32284d8a51e5bdb9534b3e57635829912","tid":1026692,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58551189143fb2e6d1f588077c6c3c66f843fb1a","tid":1026692,"uid":109515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:15:09.000Z","msg":"巴打你令我諗起幾年前美麗華出面見到架P 牌七人車，嗰日又係有雨，架車前後玻璃起曬霧，又開咗雨撥同大燈，最搞笑係線都逆埋仲要揸得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb70780fcb81280e39b0ba0387d587c18ad5944","tid":1026692,"uid":185449,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:37:03.000Z","msg":"唔好開咁凍就得"},{"pid":"773399ac63410431324701560411824290476791","tid":1026692,"uid":185449,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"如果街外濕氣重 你又開到架車冷氣好凍既話呢 你車身玻璃會加快室外空氣係你玻璃上凝結水珠既速度 呢個時候你要做既應該係開大冷氣風扇同時教返高少少冷氣溫度"},{"pid":"b111b4774c7e41dd659206d39df1cf1b67b28d3f","tid":1026692,"uid":203177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:43:22.000Z","msg":"車頭窗起霧，冷氣要較返由車頭玻璃底出 盡量吹走水氣"},{"pid":"602475efec10ac95c54a0318fce597a929b76e7c","tid":1026692,"uid":159236,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:50:41.000Z","msg":"憑感覺揸，唔駛睇得清嘅！"},{"pid":"047bd5d65107f7335cab563f8cfeb60a0785fb08","tid":1026692,"uid":31946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"認真超大雨果陣靠雨撥係無用<br />\n<br />\n我試過落埋rain x都去唔切水<br />\n<br />\n唯有渣慢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc42e6c61e3a5960eac0e93b0e2a3ea8e178bc76","tid":1026692,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"呢個情況應該係要合埋眼，用心去感受身邊環境，靠聽覺同觸覺去揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4019b1e7e8ac223b5fdc1aea065bf481a578c7","tid":1026692,"uid":233593,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:00:10.000Z","msg":"唔知你架車有無，恆溫冷氣有個mode係吹車頭玻璃俾呢啲環境用"},{"pid":"07912ca79682bc39847c5b7b9e992cc4996f4d72","tid":1026692,"uid":41154,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc42e6c61e3a5960eac0e93b0e2a3ea8e178bc76","tid":1026692,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"呢個情況應該係要合埋眼，用心去感受身邊環境，靠聽覺同觸覺去揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:03:04.000Z","msg":"邊洗用聽覺同觸覺去揸<br />\n識揸車一定係用第六感去揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34a440db24357896e750a3495930d7743f73fb8","tid":1026692,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:35:27.000Z","msg":"我都試過，上年8月勁大雨，淆到行40 50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0844b0796b3417c25985603f220cc91408a5d0fb","tid":1026692,"uid":148909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:38:50.000Z","msg":"一樣 頭先行到大埔果幾隻灣<br />\n咩都睇唔到 之後全部車要打住死火燈行<br />\n我望望地下 發現自己都踩曬界"},{"pid":"fdc69ffafb49b59e2987601621dd86ac161c5a13","tid":1026692,"uid":9115,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"習慣嫁啫<br />\n地下唔好睇條線,而係睇反光果粒釘仔<br />\n至於睇車,一樣係唔好睇架車,而係睇車燈"},{"pid":"610d86ccfd56a1d09c78206a6d521bda5408b8f9","tid":1026692,"uid":214936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:12:26.000Z","msg":"試過行老龍落大兩，對面線仲一鳩車灘水上黎，即刻有2-3秒睇唔到野，咁岩係土灣位段，真係鳩都縮一縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a118ff73b0d0e381451e2deec4487dc1f6ef89","tid":1026692,"uid":15916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"冷氣唔好吹住側邊窗 會起霧<br />\n大銀幕就山要開車果個玻璃暖氣先唔會起霧"},{"pid":"77c1833580837d4cf840b1e466704baae83f1262","tid":1026692,"uid":42629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"773399ac63410431324701560411824290476791","tid":1026692,"uid":185449,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"如果街外濕氣重 你又開到架車冷氣好凍既話呢 你車身玻璃會加快室外空氣係你玻璃上凝結水珠既速度 呢個時候你要做既應該係開大冷氣風扇同時教返高少少冷氣溫度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T17:52:39.000Z","msg":"如果係車內玻璃起霧, 係要車內熱,外面凍先會.<br />\n通常係好凍天氣, 而你車入面開左暖氣先會咁<br />\n除非樓主喺今日天氣都要開暖氣, 如果唔係唔關起霧事<br />\n係出面真係比較大雨"},{"pid":"5b2bce0bdabaf52245d4917e16b21641dde1470b","tid":1026692,"uid":21774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T17:54:34.000Z","msg":"睇唔清一撚定要同前車留多啲位<br />\n萬一地下有積水刹車距離會長好多<br />\n仲有如果係夜晚睇唔到地下既線都唔好開高燈，你睇唔到其他車都應該睇唔到你再開高燈前車更加睇唔到！"},{"pid":"4b364631a0968fb8a58d7b41b0554006766b3d04","tid":1026692,"uid":147011,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:02:51.000Z","msg":"試過落暴風雪楂，伸手不見五指，都未驚過<br />\n<br />\n但係你應該冷氣調到吹擋風玻璃，溫度校低啲，咁就唔會起霧"},{"pid":"ce8152ed9d36e831ac2cf3509f79a347c4c7aedd","tid":1026692,"uid":147011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b364631a0968fb8a58d7b41b0554006766b3d04","tid":1026692,"uid":147011,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:02:51.000Z","msg":"試過落暴風雪楂，伸手不見五指，都未驚過<br />\n<br />\n但係你應該冷氣調到吹擋風玻璃，溫度校低啲，咁就唔會起霧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:04:54.000Z","msg":"風量較大啲先啱<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}